data.description: Charming home in a quiet cul-de-sac, located in a desirable area in Lakewood. This lovely single story home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with an open living room, cozy fireplace, wood floors throughout, granite countertops in the kitchen, tile floors in both bathrooms and in the showers. A spacious backyard perfect for entertaining guests, RV parking, a covered patio and a putting green for an excellent way to improve your game skills. Conveniently located close to many shopping centers, parks, excellent schools and easy access to the freeway. All appliances are included in the sale of the property. This property is move-in ready!
